<html>
<head>
    <title>SPH Report Cleanup Information</title>
    <hta:application id="oMyApp" applicationname="SPHReportCleanupInfo" border="dialog" innerborder="no" icon="/assets/icons/favicon.ico"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/assets/styles/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" id="theme-style" href="/assets/styles/dark-theme.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/icons/favicon.ico">
    <script language="VBScript" src="/src/scripts/scripts.vbs"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to SPH Report Cleanup</h1>
        <strong class="center">Property of Ghost Hackers</strong>
        <span class="version" id="version">SPH Report Cleanup v1.2.0 &mdash; Last updated 01-09-2024</span>
        <hr>
        <h2>What is SPH Report Cleanup?</h2>
        <main>
            <p><strong>SPH Report Cleanup</strong> is a utility designed to help you keep your Downloads folder organized and secure by automatically locating and securely deleting PDF files generated by Synxis Property Hub (SPH) reports. After you print or export SPH reports, this tool ensures that any leftover PDF files are removed, protecting sensitive information and saving disk space.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Easy to Use:</strong> Simple interface and guided process.</li>
                <li><strong>Secure Deletion:</strong> Files are deleted using a secure method to prevent recovery.</li>
                <li><strong>Convenient:</strong> Optionally creates a desktop shortcut for quick access in the future.</li>
                <li><strong>Up-to-date:</strong> Checks for updates to itself and its dependencies.</li>
                <li><strong>Open Source:</strong> Fully transparent and available on GitHub.</li>
            </ul>
        </main>
        <hr>
        <h2>How to Use</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Click <strong>Continue</strong> to begin the cleanup process.</li>
            <li>Review the list of SPH PDF files found in your Downloads folder.</li>
            <li>Confirm deletion to securely remove the files.</li>
            <li>Optionally, create a desktop shortcut for future use.</li>
        </ol>
        <hr>
        <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
        <section>
            <p><strong>SPH Report Cleanup is provided as-is and without warranty.</strong> Use at your own risk. Ghost Hackers is not responsible for any data loss or damages resulting from use of this tool. Please review the full disclaimer and license on our GitHub page.</p>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <span class="center">Thank you for choosing SPH Report Cleanup. Please read the above information before continuing.</span><br>
        <span class="center">We value your feedback and are always open to suggestions.</span><br>
        <div class="buttons">
            <button onclick="Continue()" aria-label="Continue">Continue</button>
            <button onclick="DisplayReadmeMessages()" aria-label="README">README</button>
            <button onclick="EmailUs()" aria-label="Email Us">Email Us</button>
            <button onclick="ReportIssue()" aria-label="Report Issue">Report Issue</button>
            <button onclick="RequestFeature()" aria-label="Request Feature">Request Feature</button>
            <button id="theme-toggle" aria-label="Switch to Light Theme" style="margin-left:1em;font-size:1.2em;" title="Switch to Light Theme"><span id="theme-icon">üåô</span></button>
        </div>
        <div class="footer center" style="margin-top:2em;font-size:0.95em;color:var(--footer-color,#888);">
            &copy; 2025 Ghost Hackers &mdash; <a href="https://github.com/Ghost-Hackers/sph-report-cleanup" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;">GitHub</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script language="VBScript">
    Sub Continue
        ' When user clicks Continue, open DisplayInfo.hta and close this window
        Dim WshShell, displayInfoPath
        Set WshShell = CreateObject("WScript.Shell")
        displayInfoPath = "src/scripts/DisplayInfo.hta"
        WshShell.Run Chr(34) & displayInfoPath & Chr(34), 1, False
        window.close
    End Sub
    </script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        // Theme toggle logic with icon
        var isDark = true;
        var themeToggle = document.getElementById('theme-toggle');
        var themeIcon = document.getElementById('theme-icon');
        themeToggle.onclick = function() {
            var themeLink = document.getElementById('theme-style');
            if (isDark) {
                themeLink.href = '/assets/styles/light-theme.css';
                themeIcon.textContent = '‚òÄÔ∏è';
                this.ariaLabel = 'Switch to Dark Theme';
                this.title = 'Switch to Dark Theme';
            } else {
                themeLink.href = '/assets/styles/dark-theme.css';
                themeIcon.textContent = 'üåô';
                this.ariaLabel = 'Switch to Light Theme';
                this.title = 'Switch to Light Theme';
            }
            isDark = !isDark;
        };
        // Keyboard accessibility for theme toggle
        themeToggle.onkeyup = function(e) {
            if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') this.onclick();
        };
        // Focus first button for accessibility
        window.onload = function() {
            document.querySelector('.buttons button').focus();
        };
    </script>
</body>
</html>
